data.description: This single story, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home features 1651 square feet of living space. The layout features a separate dining area that leads to a nice open kitchen. Granite counter-tops in the kitchen.  The large master bedroom is just off of the family room and features a spacious walk in closet. This floor plan also includes a 2-car garage and large covered patio.  Home has an estimated completion of late November 2019.
